  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). NOTE: package was updated post-signing to incorporate supplemental mesh-refinement results without re-signing; one validation result therefore carries an evidenceTimestamp strictly later than the package signatureTimestamp.",
